value.textDescription:
@copilot_chat_finder.py go to the finder, I need to export copilot chats as they are. if  there are more than one file merge it and save in json format.

I do not need to use ChatSession or any other model classes

I need to same for @cursor_chat_finder.py 

But in case of cursor it requires different approuch since it stores data in vscdb format.

Firsly convert it to sqlite, then go to each sqlite file, fetch it content and save as it was done for other finders
